   "source": [
    "## 📊 Cálculo del Ticket Promedio (AOV)\n",
    "\n",
    "El ticket promedio (Average Order Value - AOV) representa el gasto promedio por compra realizada por los clientes.\n",
    "\n",
    "Para calcularlo:\n",
    "- Primero se calcula el ingreso total (`Revenue`) por cada orden (`InvoiceNo`)\n",
    "- Luego se obtiene el promedio de esos valores\n",
    "\n",
    "Esta métrica es clave para entender el comportamiento de compra y detectar oportunidades de crecimiento en el negocio.\n",
    "\n",
    "df['Revenue'] = df['Quantity'] * df['UnitPrice']\n",
    "aov = df.groupby('InvoiceNo')['Revenue'].sum().mean()\n",
    "print(f\"Ticket promedio: ${aov:.2f}\")\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 28,
   "id": "c87f38f0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Ticket promedio: $1308.01\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Calculamos el ticket promedio (Average Order Value - aov),\n",
    "df['Revenue'] = df['Quantity'] * df['UnitPrice']\n",
    "df.head()\n",
    "aov = df.groupby('InvoiceNo')['Revenue'].sum().mean()\n",
    "print(f\"Ticket promedio: ${aov:.2f}\")"
   ]
  },
